OL,3,GWest Midlands
OL,4,
OL,5,CToday:FBlue skies at first, before a
OL,6,Flittle cloud bubbles up through the
OL,7,Fmorning. Still plenty of sunny spells
OL,8,Fand feeling very warm with light winds.
OL,9,
OL,10,CTonight:FA dry and fine end to the day
OL,11,Fwith plenty of evening sunshine.
OL,12,FStaying dry overnight with clear
OL,13,Fspells, some patchy cloud and light
OL,14,Fwinds.
OL,15,
OL,16,CTuesday:FContinuing largely fine, dry
OL,17,Fand settled on Tuesday, skies turning
OL,18,Fa little hazy at times. Slightly
OL,19,Fwarmer than Monday.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
OL,24,ANext Page  BWeather  CReg News  FReg TV
